The paper deals with metric data structures and embeddings, which are fundamental topics in computer science. The paper is likely to be classified under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics).
